# Direct voxel slab ablation from the yhi face.
# This verifies that source-backed local ablation can choose a slab face other
# than the default xlo direction.

units si

voxel material carbon density 1800.0
voxel create solid slab nx 4 ny 8 nz 4 dx 1.0e-6 material carbon

source q1 constant 1.8 units kg/m2/s
timestep mass/courant 0.5 source q1

stats 1
stats_style step time active-voxels deleted-voxels remaining-mass mass-fraction

variable i loop 8
label ablate-loop
voxel ablate solid source q1 policy local face yhi delete yes
run 1
next i
jump SELF ablate-loop

verify remaining-mass exact "initial-mass - q1*(nx*nz*dx*dx)*time" tolerance 0.01 percent norm max
verify mass-fraction exact "1.0 - q1*time/(rho*ny*dx)" tolerance 0.01 percent norm max
verify deleted-voxels exact "64" tolerance 0.01 absolute norm final
